manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:

[android:allowBackup=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: This flag allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup=true]

You can decide which site loads when starts: By long pressing an entry in the overview (Startsite, Bookmarks, History) you can choose it. Over the menu of the overview you can also set a blank favorite.

Menus and dialogs
All menus and dialogs are opened at the bottom of the screen. If the dialog is large you will first see only the upper part. If you swipe it up, the rest will get visible.
You can close them by pressing the back button, swiping them down or by clicking outside

Long press
If you long press the menu icon or the "Navigation button", the "Fast toggle dialog" will show. If you long press the "Bookmark icon", the "Filter dialog" will show."

playstore_details.title: Turbo Browser- Fast And Secure with Ad Block
playstore_details.description:
The smallest, fastest, secure Browser;
It is specifically designed for mobile phones and tablet, brings you an amazing Premium web experience.

It is based off the Android WebKit Engine.

Key Features:
- Tabbed Internet Browsing
- Incognito Mode. Private browse the web without saving any browser history.
- Supports Adobe Flash Player
- The fastest Start Times: View web pages quicker on your phone
- Block Ads
- Homepage: Add favorite links to your homepage with a single click and access sites easily from your mobile desktop;
- Bookmarks
- History
- Find in Page
- Super easy copy/paste
- Small Footprint
- Quick search: most popular default search engines
- Advanced Gesture feature
- Sharing - Super-easy and intuitive ways to share mobile contents through social media channels.
- Advanced Settings
- Custom download location
